{"tid":1003184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局：2016年後再次錄得負資產個案","createTime":"2019-01-31T12:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T12:44:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3be65f85b6b90ffbce72ce27378a81fa76922519","tid":1003184,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190131/s00010/5ef6fb37cf238cc55446d70de78600cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190131%2Fs00010%2F5ef6fb37cf238cc55446d70de78600cf.jpg&h=58fd2c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金管局公布，2018年第4季負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數為262宗，這是自從2016年第4季以來再次錄得負資產個案。這些個案涉及銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款或按揭保險計劃的貸款，而這類貸款的按揭成數一般較高。<br />\n<br />\n2018年第4季的負資產住宅按揭貸款所涉及的金額為11.89億元。負資產住宅按揭貸款中無抵押部分的金額為5800萬元。<br />\n<br />\n銀行自從2011年第1季起，並無錄得任何拖欠3個月以上的負資產住宅按揭貸款紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n金管局指出，此調查所得數字僅涉及銀行提供並已知道為負資產的一按貸款（即欠受訪機構的未償還貸款額超過按揭物業的當前市值），當中並不包括涉及二按，而連同二按計算屬於負資產貸款的住宅按揭貸款。由於銀行沒有客戶在二按下的未償還貸款的資料，因此無法知悉其中有多少宗屬於負資產貸款。"},{"pid":"3355fdb79b40a5f2d1626d6d4df84fd29e393e05","tid":1003184,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"呼氣&hellip;&hellip;吸氣&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9a43d90c002fd278f23c56fa6f7b7f25b12062ba","tid":1003184,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"無野無野，家陣吹緊唔會Call Loan，有份工供得起就無野"},{"pid":"d30f6619fc3607eb5b7688618fd76ee8dd4e2479","tid":1003184,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3355fdb79b40a5f2d1626d6d4df84fd29e393e05","tid":1003184,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"呼氣&hellip;&hellip;吸氣&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100114/photo/0114-00176-036b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100114%2Fphoto%2F0114-00176-036b1.jpg&h=d3423cdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0332a5ab6784a821ddcc45a06f8081d04f4eaf46","tid":1003184,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a43d90c002fd278f23c56fa6f7b7f25b12062ba","tid":1003184,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"無野無野，家陣吹緊唔會Call Loan，有份工供得起就無野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"我記得98金融風暴至沙士時<br />\n係會CALL"}]}